{"tid":1347593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【回帶】梁天琦激勵演說","createTime":"2019-07-22T06:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T04:17:19.000Z","uid":180201,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8cef78e82a828192148c0b80135a2b67cd7f8441","tid":1347593,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:23:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2136822073313759/videos/909713482696462/UzpfSTEwMDM3NTU1MDIyOToxMDE2MjE4NDAxMTAxNTIzMA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2136822073313759%2Fvideos%2F909713482696462%2FUzpfSTEwMDM3NTU1MDIyOToxMDE2MjE4NDAxMTAxNTIzMA%2F&d=wUVL7ECAGG5qyTf5%2FTxhHyVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=3d2c9362\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2136822073313759/videos/909713482696462/UzpfSTEwMDM3NTU1MDIyOToxMDE2MjE4NDAxMTAxNTIzMA/</a><br />\n<br />\n當年行得前嘅政治人物，因為香港嘅未來，因為我地，依家坐緊監。<br />\n佢地用佢地人生保貴嘅黃金時間，換取香港人嘅覺醒。<br />\n被政治監禁嘅人，我地一定會救返你地，係未？<br />\n革命，一定會有流血、會失敗同一定有人會死。<br />\n但今時今日，我地依家比政府、黑警同社團欺壓到上心口。<br />\n一定有好多人好唔舒服，好嬲，我都係。<br />\n<br />\n我好嬲好唔開心，我都唔知可以做啲咩。<br />\n依家香港有法律？有警察保護？依家咩都無。<br />\n我地再同政府講法律、道理已經無用。<br />\n大家今朝直播都見到，何妖、建制、警察講野幾咁無理、仆街。<br />\n<br />\n我開呢個post係想做啲野，但我又唔知可以點做。<br />\n希望大家守望相助，身邊有朋友情緒唔太好就安慰下佢。<br />\n我都好唔開心好嬲。<br />\n<br />\n我打呢篇野係想發洩下，同希望大家重記得天琦。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人加油</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6928fe392e19b7bf1e80b40c42fadf83dda0795c","tid":1347593,"uid":180201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:26:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家加油<br />\n727企出黎<br />\n香港加油<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ce3f220be69de634f8fe9ec316a81d8214eae27c","tid":1347593,"uid":5523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:03:04.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n主權在民<br />\n以武制暴"},{"pid":"59fb38a2e7b7a5b060972c1f2aea47736b99b482","tid":1347593,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:04:06.000Z","msg":"全港抗爭者都講緊你果句<br />\n光復香港，時代革命呀天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aacf3ee23afcf99d9a9ad18d8880d5c938d78f06","tid":1347593,"uid":5523,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"59fb38a2e7b7a5b060972c1f2aea47736b99b482","tid":1347593,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:04:06.000Z","msg":"全港抗爭者都講緊你果句<br />\n光復香港，時代革命呀天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:05:42.000Z","msg":"我做左20幾年人<br />\n只有佢令我覺得有人代表緊我<br />\n我仲生存緊<br />\n我唔係痴線"},{"pid":"a0fa9a33ddd585c6b1fa99fab4e72fbb61fc31e3","tid":1347593,"uid":58266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:12:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22dc8837e7f80f7d1bda5d24cc8103649c7b17c4","tid":1347593,"uid":60749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:12:55.000Z","msg":"你要堅持自己相信嘅嘢<br />\n唔好去阻止人哋堅持嘅嗰套<br />\n同時唔好俾人阻止同動搖到<br />\n而只要大家目標相同<br />\n就應該要支持大家 不論手法"},{"pid":"0a42632e4d56ca37c6a17d933c8dde4ee708982d","tid":1347593,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aacf3ee23afcf99d9a9ad18d8880d5c938d78f06","tid":1347593,"uid":5523,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"59fb38a2e7b7a5b060972c1f2aea47736b99b482","tid":1347593,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:04:06.000Z","msg":"全港抗爭者都講緊你果句<br />\n光復香港，時代革命呀天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:05:42.000Z","msg":"我做左20幾年人<br />\n只有佢令我覺得有人代表緊我<br />\n我仲生存緊<br />\n我